00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,270
Give me that. I'll give it to him.

448
00:38:45,780 --> 00:38:46,880
No, I don't want to.

449
00:38:56,290 --> 00:38:58,660
There's a way you can meet Jae Hyun every day.

450
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:02,090
Join our club.

451
00:39:02,690 --> 00:39:03,990
What kind of club is it?

452
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:06,430
Solidarity of Philosophy. It's a philosophy club.

453
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,260
What a name.

454
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:09,670
The name is a bit pretentious,

455
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:11,430
but we just study philosophy there.

456
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:12,800
I don't know much about philosophy.

457
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,500
We don't know much either.

458
00:39:14,570 --> 00:39:16,140
That's why we meet up and study.

459
00:39:17,370 --> 00:39:20,040
This club isn't strictly for law majors. It's a college club.

460
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:21,440
You can join if you want.

461
00:39:22,350 --> 00:39:23,750
Jae Hyun is the principal assistant administrator,

462
00:39:23,750 --> 00:39:25,210
so he attends the seminar every week.

463
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:28,650
He's actually in the club room more than the room for law majors.

464
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:30,590
Really?

465
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:33,820
(Books for Today)

466
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:37,090
We write down where we'll meet on this board.

467
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:41,130
That's Jae Hyun's.

468
00:39:42,530 --> 00:39:44,400
Jae Hyun drinks at the bar often.

469
00:39:46,370 --> 00:39:48,470
I'll know where he is once I look at this board.

470
00:39:48,570 --> 00:39:51,410
Some people write in code not to give away where they are.

471
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:53,910
But usually, everyone is welcomed.

472
00:39:54,240 --> 00:39:55,910
It's more like, "Come if you want to drink."

473
00:39:55,910 --> 00:39:57,150
"Let's drink until we drop."

