499
00:43:40,350 --> 00:43:43,090
I keep standing on my toes

500
00:43:44,320 --> 00:43:46,420
Yet I still do not see you

501
00:43:50,030 --> 00:43:52,190
At times when the waiting grows longer

502
00:43:53,530 --> 00:43:55,400
