00:45:30,690 --> 00:45:31,990
Is something wrong?

512
00:45:34,230 --> 00:45:35,560
What is it?

513
00:45:38,600 --> 00:45:40,470
I'm trying to decide...

514
00:45:42,810 --> 00:45:44,570
what to tell you first.

515
00:45:49,510 --> 00:45:50,850
I've decided.

516
00:45:51,250 --> 00:45:52,350
Hurry up.

517
00:45:55,790 --> 00:45:57,720
Young Min will be back in two days,

518
00:45:58,090 --> 00:45:59,890
and I still haven't gone grocery shopping.

519
00:46:01,090 --> 00:46:02,430
Come on, you...

520
00:46:03,130 --> 00:46:05,130
I should go before they close.

521
00:46:24,110 --> 00:46:26,580
She hasn't changed a bit.

522
00:46:27,350 --> 00:46:30,320
Why isn't she wearing any gloves?

523
00:46:31,720 --> 00:46:33,660
And her jacket is too thin.

524
00:46:33,660 --> 00:46:36,890
(3 Ice creams for 1 dollar, Soda for 1.5 dollars)

525
00:46:40,300 --> 00:46:41,460
Goodness.

526
00:46:42,770 --> 00:46:44,030
Who is this for?

527
00:46:44,500 --> 00:46:45,630
It's for me.

528
00:46:46,140 --> 00:46:47,900
Gosh, why?

529
00:46:47,900 --> 00:46:50,710
Why would a lady need to drink that much?

530
00:46:52,010 --> 00:46:53,280
Then what am I supposed to do?

531
00:46:53,280 --> 00:46:54,340
Do what?

532
00:46:54,340 --> 00:46:56,310
I already have a hard time falling asleep,

533
00:46:57,180 --> 00:46:59,050
