534
00:46:59,450 --> 00:47:00,520
Why?

535
00:47:00,980 --> 00:47:03,020
I shouldn't be acting like this.

536
00:47:03,690 --> 00:47:06,520
I need to get a grip, but it keeps coming back to me.

537
00:47:08,460 --> 00:47:10,630
It's driving me crazy!

538
00:47:46,560 --> 00:47:47,900
Where are you?

539
00:47:48,030 --> 00:47:50,030
Did you fall in a well or something?

540
00:47:50,030 --> 00:47:52,740
Why aren't you back? Why?

541
00:47:52,940 --> 00:47:55,200
Hurry up, already!

542
00:48:03,280 --> 00:48:04,450
Thank you.

543
00:48:07,750 --> 00:48:09,620
Here. Oh, gosh.

