00:48:16,730 --> 00:48:17,990
This is heavy.

547
00:48:20,560 --> 00:48:22,570
Oh, thank you.

548
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:24,270
No problem.

549
00:48:24,270 --> 00:48:27,440
Have we met before?

550
00:48:27,440 --> 00:48:29,970
I have a common-looking face, so I'm used to that.

551
00:48:29,970 --> 00:48:31,670
You don't look so common.

552
00:48:32,140 --> 00:48:34,410
Oh, really?

553
00:48:35,540 --> 00:48:38,350
I wonder why everyone says so. That's odd.

554
00:48:41,950 --> 00:48:43,690
Goodbye, then.

555
00:48:59,070 --> 00:49:00,770
- Good job. - No problem, sir.

556
00:49:01,940 --> 00:49:03,710
She went inside. Should we go?

557
00:49:05,270 --> 00:49:06,810
- Yes, let's go. - All right.

558
00:49:07,680 --> 00:49:11,210
May I ask how you know her?

559
00:49:11,210 --> 00:49:12,650
No, you may not.

560
00:49:12,880 --> 00:49:13,950
Yes, sir.

561
00:49:14,780 --> 00:49:16,720
- Hey, Jun Woo. - Yes, sir?

562
00:49:16,720 --> 00:49:18,720
Could you come straight here in the morning...

563
00:49:18,720 --> 00:49:20,090
for a few days?

564
00:49:20,890 --> 00:49:22,590
- Sorry? - See where she's headed...

565
00:49:22,590 --> 00:49:24,090
and what she's doing.

566
00:49:25,690 --> 00:49:26,800
Yes, sir.

567
00:49:27,830 --> 00:49:29,800
It's not stalking, and it's not a crime.

568
00:49:30,030 --> 00:49:32,700
Just think of it as good will.

569
00:49:32,870 --> 00:49:34,100
All right, sir.

570
00:49:37,610 --> 00:49:38,910
I know her from college.

571
00:49:39,710 --> 00:49:41,580
She was a nice, smart kid.

572
00:49:58,660 --> 00:50:01,300
(To Jae Hyun)

573
00:50:45,570 --> 00:50:47,880
(Thanks to those moments that were as pretty as flowers,)

574
00:50:47,880 --> 00:50:49,880
(I think I can go on. Sorry and thank you. Jae Hyun.)

575
00:51:44,730 --> 00:51:47,070
These are the gloves you were looking for, sir.

576
00:51:47,340 --> 00:51:49,170
They are all new this season.

577
00:51:49,340 --> 00:51:50,440
Okay.

578
00:51:50,740 --> 00:51:52,540
Are they for your wife?

579
00:51:52,710 --> 00:51:53,880
No.

580
00:51:54,010 --> 00:51:56,150
Oh... All right, sir.

581
00:51:56,480 --> 00:51:58,510
You don't have to tell her, either.

582
00:51:59,050 --> 00:52:00,880
Of course, sir.

583
00:52:01,080 --> 00:52:02,320
I'll take these.

584
00:52:03,590 --> 00:52:04,650
Yes, sir.

585
00:52:15,160 --> 00:52:16,230
Yes?

586
00:52:16,500 --> 00:52:17,630
Mr. Han.

587
00:52:17,630 --> 00:52:19,170
Are you doing your job?

588
00:52:19,170 --> 00:52:20,400
I am, but...

589
00:52:20,400 --> 00:52:21,640
Ms. Yoon is...

590
00:52:21,640 --> 00:52:22,740
Is what?

591
00:52:23,210 --> 00:52:25,010
She's at the office, sir.

592
00:52:25,240 --> 00:52:26,240
What?

593
00:52:26,580 --> 00:52:29,180
(Cancel the unfair dismissal!)

594
00:52:32,110 --> 00:52:35,350
Young Min, how long are you going to keep ignoring my messages?

595
00:52:35,780 --> 00:52:37,850
This is foul play.

596
00:52:46,330 --> 00:52:48,730
(Cancel the unfair dismissal! Murderous Company, Hyung Sung Group)

597
00:52:50,730 --> 00:52:52,370
Should we keep watch?

598
00:52:52,940 --> 00:52:54,200
Forget it.

599
00:52:54,440 --> 00:52:55,470
Yes, sir.

600
00:52:55,640 --> 00:52:58,070
Good will, my foot. This is stalking.

601
00:52:59,980 --> 00:53:01,780
I'm sorry for asking you to do this.

602
00:53:01,780 --> 00:53:03,650
It's nothing, sir.

603
00:53:06,320 --> 00:53:08,750
Should I cancel the meeting you had today?

604
00:53:08,750 --> 00:53:11,020
- What meeting? - With the head of Seoul Bank.

605
00:53:13,320 --> 00:53:15,120
- I still have to work. - Yes, sir.

606
00:53:26,900 --> 00:53:27,940
You're right.

607
00:53:30,570 --> 00:53:31,870
"Three handsome sons-in-law..."

608
00:53:31,870 --> 00:53:33,710
"of conglomerate families everyone wants to date..."

609
00:53:34,110 --> 00:53:35,410
Whatever.

610
00:53:35,780 --> 00:53:37,680
He has a great figure. He could be an actor.

611
00:53:37,680 --> 00:53:40,180
He's still young, and he's already a vice-president.

612
00:53:40,180 --> 00:53:42,550
- Haven't you heard? - What?

613
00:53:43,150 --> 00:53:45,420
He's Jang Seo Kyung's husband.

614
00:53:45,450 --> 00:53:48,390
- Jang Seo Kyung. - You're right!

615
00:53:48,920 --> 00:53:51,230
The chairman was against the marriage,

616
00:53:51,530 --> 00:53:54,960
but Jang Seo Kyung caused a fit...

617
00:53:54,960 --> 00:53:56,400
and managed to make it work.

618
00:53:56,700 --> 00:53:59,500
He went to jail for the chairman and recently got discharged.

619
00:53:59,500 --> 00:54:00,940
- Really? - Let me see.

620
00:54:00,940 --> 00:54:02,870
- It says so here. - Give it!

621
00:54:02,870 --> 00:54:04,640
- Where? - Let go!

622
00:54:04,640 --> 00:54:06,580
- Gosh, what's wrong with you? - That hurt!

623
00:54:06,580 --> 00:54:07,910
- I couldn't see. - Goodness!

624
00:54:07,910 --> 00:54:10,280
- You could've waited your turn! - Gosh!

625
00:54:15,420 --> 00:54:17,390
(Three handsome sons-in-law of conglomerate families...)

626
00:54:17,390 --> 00:54:19,590
(everyone wants to date, Han Jae Hyun of Hyung Sung Group)

627
00:54:26,160 --> 00:54:28,160
(The marriage between the chairman's daughter and a mere employee)

628
00:54:51,690 --> 00:54:53,860
I will never agree on a settlement.

629
00:54:54,490 --> 00:54:56,830
Set up the School Violence Committee.

630
00:54:57,260 --> 00:54:58,290
But...

631
00:54:58,930 --> 00:55:00,960
Mr. Han said to never allow...

632
00:55:00,960 --> 00:55:04,170
And you should have stopped him.

633
00:55:04,330 --> 00:55:06,640
Even if it were Jun Seo's grandfather who came,

634
00:55:06,640 --> 00:55:09,100
- you should've stopped it. - I'm sorry, ma'am.

635
00:55:09,940 --> 00:55:12,310
I did tell him that we can't do that,

636
00:55:12,770 --> 00:55:14,610
but he insisted, saying he's a young boy.

637
00:55:14,610 --> 00:55:16,850
I don't want you to misunderstand me.

638
00:55:17,010 --> 00:55:19,210
Even if my son wasn't the victim,

639
00:55:19,210 --> 00:55:21,320
I would've wanted you to go by the rules.

640
00:55:21,480 --> 00:55:22,950
If we just let this pass,

641
00:55:22,950 --> 00:55:25,150
it will only humiliate the school.

642
00:55:26,390 --> 00:55:28,590
This school should be special, don't you think?

643
00:55:29,090 --> 00:55:30,760
Isn't that why parents...

644
00:55:30,760 --> 00:55:33,860
want to send their kids here at all costs?

645
00:55:36,030 --> 00:55:39,640
And it's also why I make such large donations here.

646
00:55:49,580 --> 00:55:51,580
(Han Jae Hyun of Hyung Sung Group)

647
00:55:51,580 --> 00:55:53,520
(The marriage between the chairman's daughter and a mere employee)

648
00:56:11,300 --> 00:56:12,330
Yes?

649
00:56:12,330 --> 00:56:14,440
I don't know what to tell you.

650
00:56:15,340 --> 00:56:16,510
Is something wrong?

651
00:56:17,110 --> 00:56:20,240
I think the School Violence Committee will be set up.

652
00:56:21,510 --> 00:56:22,640
Why, all of a sudden?

653
00:56:23,480 --> 00:56:26,180
Jun Seo's mother came to see us.

654
00:56:29,280 --> 00:56:33,160
She told us not to give you...

655
00:56:33,420 --> 00:56:34,890
her number.

656
00:56:35,120 --> 00:56:38,630
I don't think she wants to agree on a settlement.

657
00:56:38,630 --> 00:56:39,630
I see.

658
00:56:41,030 --> 00:56:42,130
What about...

659
00:56:43,300 --> 00:56:44,770
his father's number?

660
00:56:45,030 --> 00:56:46,840
- He said he would give... - I'm sorry.

661
00:56:46,840 --> 00:56:50,010
We can't give you that, either.

662
00:56:50,410 --> 00:56:52,340
- I'm really sorry. - Then...

663
00:56:53,910 --> 00:56:55,710
when will it be held?

664
00:57:03,350 --> 00:57:06,460
This will be a great opportunity for Seoul Bank as well.

665
00:57:06,820 --> 00:57:09,360
All right. Let's get it started.

666
00:57:09,620 --> 00:57:10,630
Thank you, sir.

667
00:57:14,730 --> 00:57:16,500
Go ahead. Take it.

668
00:57:17,070 --> 00:57:18,100
Excuse me.

669
00:57:21,870 --> 00:57:23,370
Yes? What is it?

670
00:57:23,770 --> 00:57:25,940
Dad, are you with Mom?

671
00:57:26,480 --> 00:57:27,510
No, why?

672
00:57:27,910 --> 00:57:30,850
I wanted to ask Mom what she said.

673
00:57:33,080 --> 00:57:34,150
What do you mean?

674
00:57:34,450 --> 00:57:36,650
They're going to hold the School Violence Committee...

675
00:57:36,650 --> 00:57:37,990
because of Mom.

676
00:57:40,160 --> 00:57:43,390
Yes. The head of Seoul Bank?

677
00:57:45,860 --> 00:57:46,860
All right.

678
00:57:48,630 --> 00:57:50,570
What is he up to?

679
00:57:56,100 --> 00:57:58,940
Excuse me. May I see Ms. Jang?

680
00:57:58,940 --> 00:58:00,140
Do you have an appointment?

681
00:58:00,980 --> 00:58:02,640
- Not really... - Then no, ma'am.

682
00:58:02,640 --> 00:58:04,050
You need to make an appointment.

683
00:58:04,650 --> 00:58:06,480
Is she in, though?

684
00:58:06,480 --> 00:58:07,820
I can't tell you, ma'am.

685
00:58:09,480 --> 00:58:10,490
Then...

686
00:58:11,250 --> 00:58:13,660
- What about Mr. Han? - It will be the same, ma'am.

687
00:58:13,860 --> 00:58:15,860
You cannot see them unless you have an appointment.

688
00:58:17,190 --> 00:58:18,260
Hey!

689
00:58:19,490 --> 00:58:20,500
What is it?

690
00:58:21,130 --> 00:58:22,330
What's wrong?

691
00:58:22,800 --> 00:58:24,300
You can't do this here.

692
00:58:24,930 --> 00:58:27,100
No, I'm not here because of the protest.

693
00:58:27,300 --> 00:58:28,770
Please let me call them, at least.

694
00:58:29,000 --> 00:58:30,740
You can't do this here. Please step outside.

695
00:58:30,740 --> 00:58:32,640
- No, I... - Please leave.

696
00:58:33,010 --> 00:58:34,310
- I... - Come, ma'am.

697
00:58:34,610 --> 00:58:35,710
What do you think you're doing?

698
00:58:36,650 --> 00:58:39,450
I told you not to change the decision.

699
00:58:39,920 --> 00:58:41,050
Why shouldn't I?

700
00:58:41,250 --> 00:58:43,650
It wasn't serious enough to ruin someone's life.

701
00:58:43,650 --> 00:58:45,220
You fire employees...

702
00:58:45,350 --> 00:58:46,760
and sue them for interfering...

703
00:58:46,760 --> 00:58:48,720
with your business so easily.

704
00:58:49,060 --> 00:58:50,830
Why are you worried about his life?

705
00:58:51,090 --> 00:58:52,190
He's a young boy.

706
00:58:53,060 --> 00:58:54,200
He's just 14.

707
00:58:54,400 --> 00:58:56,900
I'm sure you fired a truckload of people...

708
00:58:57,430 --> 00:58:59,270
who have kids that are younger.

709
00:59:00,740 --> 00:59:02,270
I'm saying we should play it by the rules.

710
00:59:02,640 --> 00:59:04,070
I'm not trying to teach the kid...

711
00:59:04,070 --> 00:59:05,870
who hit my baby a lesson.

712
00:59:07,580 --> 00:59:10,080
Well, I guess I can't say it's 100 percent not that.

713
00:59:20,120 --> 00:59:21,190
So, Young Min.

714
00:59:22,320 --> 00:59:24,660
Please tell me why you did it.

715
00:59:25,290 --> 00:59:28,160
I don't care if they hold the committee.

716
00:59:29,060 --> 00:59:30,570
Of course, you do.

717
00:59:31,430 --> 00:59:32,770
You said you liked school.

718
00:59:32,930 --> 00:59:34,840
You liked your teachers and said the class was fun.

719
00:59:36,100 --> 00:59:37,140
Young Min.

720
00:59:37,570 --> 00:59:40,340
I really don't believe you did anything wrong.

721
00:59:41,040 --> 00:59:44,250
I was just annoyed. At everything.

722
00:59:45,080 --> 00:59:46,080
"Just"?

723
00:59:47,380 --> 00:59:49,220
You did it without a reason?

724
00:59:49,720 --> 00:59:51,290
I'm almost in the eighth grade.

725
00:59:52,650 --> 00:59:53,960
I will be, soon.

726
00:59:55,460 --> 00:59:58,230
They say kids get moody then.

727
00:59:58,560 --> 01:00:01,100
Says who? That doesn't even make any sense!

728
01:00:01,100 --> 01:00:04,570
Isn't Dad coming tomorrow? What do I do?

729
01:00:36,000 --> 01:00:40,970
(Mom)

730
01:00:47,310 --> 01:00:50,550
(Mom...)

731
01:01:08,300 --> 01:01:09,300
(Building 2)

732
01:01:25,750 --> 01:01:26,980
Where's Seo Kyung?

733
01:01:27,720 --> 01:01:30,150
She just left for the school, sir.

734
01:02:04,420 --> 01:02:05,750
Don't worry, ma'am.

735
01:02:06,190 --> 01:02:09,060
We'll be careful not to let any rumors out.

736
01:02:10,560 --> 01:02:11,760
Of course, you should.

737
01:02:11,960 --> 01:02:14,760
It's just as embarrassing to be known as the victim.

738
01:02:19,600 --> 01:02:20,670
Ms. Yoon.

739
01:02:42,420 --> 01:02:43,560
I beg of you, ma'am.

740
01:02:44,330 --> 01:02:45,830
Please reconsider it.

741
01:02:46,660 --> 01:02:48,500
- The boy's future... - I'm doing this...

742
01:02:48,500 --> 01:02:50,170
for the boy's future, ma'am.

743
01:02:51,400 --> 01:02:52,700
Isn't it the adults' duty...

744
01:02:52,700 --> 01:02:55,100
to tell them what's right and wrong?

745
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:58,370
It can't be good for his education...

746
01:02:58,370 --> 01:03:00,040
if we let it slide without punishment...

747
01:03:00,280 --> 01:03:02,310
when he committed a crime, don't you think?

748
01:03:03,210 --> 01:03:05,250
And for the other students, as well.

749
01:03:07,050 --> 01:03:08,080
If...

750
01:03:10,250 --> 01:03:12,390
the reason you're trying to hold...

751
01:03:13,250 --> 01:03:15,920
the committee is because it's your son...

752
01:03:15,990 --> 01:03:17,090
What did you say?

753
01:03:18,360 --> 01:03:20,900
Please take it out on me.

754
01:03:22,000 --> 01:03:23,800
It's my fault...

755
01:03:24,200 --> 01:03:25,800
for raising him poorly.

756
01:03:26,170 --> 01:03:27,940
You can take it out on me...

757
01:03:28,400 --> 01:03:29,970
however you like.

758
01:03:35,040 --> 01:03:38,180
However I like?

759
01:03:40,080 --> 01:03:42,650
Yes, ma'am. However.

760
01:03:46,690 --> 01:03:50,390
Then let's see what you can do...

761
01:03:50,860 --> 01:03:52,690
to relieve my anger.

762
01:04:31,400 --> 01:04:32,830
Please, ma'am.

763
01:04:33,940 --> 01:04:35,270
Forgive him...

764
01:04:36,340 --> 01:04:37,770
just this once.

765
01:04:53,020 --> 01:04:54,260
Please get up.

766
01:04:55,090 --> 01:04:57,690
What do you think you're doing?

767
01:04:57,960 --> 01:04:59,960
Get up, Yoon Ji Su!

768
01:05:45,470 --> 01:05:47,440
(When My Love Blooms)

769
01:05:48,980 --> 01:05:50,780
I can't help but think of the old days.

770
01:05:52,610 --> 01:05:53,650
Ji Su!

771
01:05:55,250 --> 01:05:56,880
It's been so long.

772
01:06:02,260 --> 01:06:03,760
Good luck, Ji Su.

773
01:06:04,630 --> 01:06:07,830
Just keep in mind that I'll be watching her.

774
01:06:08,200 --> 01:06:09,660
Are you asking me to leave them?

775
01:06:09,660 --> 01:06:11,830
I don't want you to suffer.

776
01:06:12,700 --> 01:06:13,770
No.

777
01:06:15,940 --> 01:06:17,110
I want to protect you.

